The plan of the exfiltration expert Tony Mendez required collaboration of Hollywood.
In order to make the story more credible, specialized magazines were state of this film project, press conferences were organized and a fictitious production company had real offices.
The details of the operation remained secret for a long time, the film is based on the memories of Tony Mendez.
The film is an unusual combination of Affleck of several genres.
