Successive moods: Documentary-style footage of Tehran (in the subtitled sequences are presented iconic photographs of the era of events and how, through these photos, these same situations have been recorded in the film, there is no big differences)
Lighter passages of Hollywood, treated with irony and a bit of exaggeration.
